  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive relentless waves of enemies and master the art of combat!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat</h2>Fight Ascension is a game inspired by Arena Shooters but focused on melee combat, featuring manual mechanics that give the player full control over every movement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Sentinel Ignis, a warrior who wields fire to battle his foes. Trapped in an arena filled with humanoid monsters, your goal is to survive as long as possible and reach increasingly challenging stages!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/58a7f4446129c614d9338902c0febb7f.poster.avif?t=1748880139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/58a7f4446129c614d9338902c0febb7f.webm?t=1748880139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/58a7f4446129c614d9338902c0febb7f.mp4?t=1748880139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enhancements</h2>Defeat enemies to earn points and acquire new abilities and enhancements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/e5a6ad9b3a1030c1801db66fcd532091.poster.avif?t=1748880139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/e5a6ad9b3a1030c1801db66fcd532091.webm?t=1748880139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/e5a6ad9b3a1030c1801db66fcd532091.mp4?t=1748880139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive relentless waves of enemies and master the art of combat!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combat</h2>Fight Ascension is a game inspired by Arena Shooters but focused on melee combat, featuring manual mechanics that give the player full control over every movement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Sentinel Ignis, a warrior who wields fire to battle his foes. Trapped in an arena filled with humanoid monsters, your goal is to survive as long as possible and reach increasingly challenging stages!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/58a7f4446129c614d9338902c0febb7f.poster.avif?t=1748880139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/58a7f4446129c614d9338902c0febb7f.webm?t=1748880139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/58a7f4446129c614d9338902c0febb7f.mp4?t=1748880139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enhancements</h2>Defeat enemies to earn points and acquire new abilities and enhancements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/e5a6ad9b3a1030c1801db66fcd532091.poster.avif?t=1748880139\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/e5a6ad9b3a1030c1801db66fcd532091.webm?t=1748880139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3505690/extras/e5a6ad9b3a1030c1801db66fcd532091.mp4?t=1748880139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>